remarks.format: ## Remarks 在将多个项添加到堆栈时，使用 PushRange 比 一次使用一个项更为有效。When adding multiple items to the stack, using PushRange is a more efficient mechanism than using one item at a time. 此外，PushRange 保证将以原子方式添加所有元素，这意味着任何其他线程都不能在所推送的元素之间注入元素。Additionally, PushRange guarantees that all of the elements will be added atomically, meaning that no other threads will be able to inject elements between the elements being pushed. 数组中较低索引处的项 `items` 将被推送到较高索引处的项之前。Items at lower indices in the `items` array will be pushed before items at higher indices. 有关代码示例，请参阅 。For a code example, see .
